//000000000000a:40:{s:2:"id";s:5:"28660";s:4:"body";s:486:"甲、乙、丙、丁四个队共同植树造林，甲队造林的亩数是另外三个队造林总亩数的&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/body2/65db35ffffb679177c8f5be277fed456_0.png" />，乙队造林的亩数是另外三个队造林总亩数的&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/body2/04738459088b4bd6294889eb205e5b97_1.png" />，丙队造林的亩数是另外三个队造林总亩数的一半，己知丁队共造林3900亩，问甲队共造林多少亩?（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）";s:7:"bd_desc";s:77:"65db35ffffb679177c8f5be277fed456_0.png|04738459088b4bd6294889eb205e5b97_1.png";s:7:"options";s:109:"[{"cs":"A ", "text":"9000"},{"cs":"B ", "text":"3600"},{"cs":"C ", "text":"6000"},{"cs":"D ", "text":"4500"}]";s:11:"description";s:612:"设甲、乙、丙、丁四个队共同植树x亩，则甲队造林&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/7fad7f0653ea668747c3461effa18302_0.png" />亩，乙队造林&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/a17086af5302de23aaec6f034c7ff821_1.png" />亩，丙队造林&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/7b7793a644bacd5158cb835a46daac55_2.png" />亩，则&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/e7b5742e1f55d8b66cc2b2af5ab2f3c5_3.png" />，解得x＝18000。所以，甲队造林18000×&nbsp;<img src="/Uploads/xingce/desc2/ddaee76e728f4a7561a2f62e37b7b9d3_4.png" /> ＝3600（亩）。因此，本题选择B选项。";s:7:"dp_desc";s:194:"7fad7f0653ea668747c3461effa18302_0.png|a17086af5302de23aaec6f034c7ff821_1.png|7b7793a644bacd5158cb835a46daac55_2.png|e7b5742e1f55d8b66cc2b2af5ab2f3c5_3.png|ddaee76e728f4a7561a2f62e37b7b9d3_4.png";s:6:"answer";s:1:"B";s:8:"wrongans";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:10:"optiontype";s:1:"1";s:8:"bigtype1";s:12:"数量关系";s:10:"smalltype1";s:12:"数学运算";s:10:"pointtype1";s:18:"一元一次方程";s:5:"tagid";s:1:"0";s:6:"chance";s:1:"0";s:6:"ismock";s:1:"1";s:5:"qyear";s:4:"2009";s:5:"views";s:1:"0";s:6:"rorate";s:1:"0";s:7:"usetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"materialid";s:1:"0";s:4:"diff";s:1:"0";s:7:"addtime";s:1:"0";s:10:"updatetime";s:1:"0";s:10:"supplierid";s:1:"2";s:8:"sourceid";s:5:"55297";s:8:"insertid";s:1:"0";s:6:"extend";s:4:"null";s:5:"skill";s:46:"<p class="item-p">列方程法、比例法</p>";s:7:"bigtype";s:1:"2";s:9:"smalltype";s:2:"68";s:9:"pointtype";s:2:"76";s:6:"tagids";N;s:7:"errnums";s:1:"0";s:8:"collects